  "body": "This issue tracks the 2 critical bug fixes pointed out by Paul from Lighthouse and Danny from EF. They Currently don't impact our run time so we have some leeway before fixing them.\r\n\r\n\r\n| Descriptions  | Eth2.0 spec PR   | Prysm PR   |\r\n|------------ | ------------- |-------------|\r\n|Fix circular dependency when embedding block roots in state by using signed_root(block) | [716](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/716) |   |\r\n| Fix start shard order of operations  | [821](https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/pull/821)  |  |\r\n\r\nReference: https://github.com/ethereum/eth2.0-specs/releases/tag/v0.5.1",
